text.section:
A notice under subsection (a) of this section shall include:
The name and address of the party seeking to create the lien;
A statement of intent to create a lien;
An identification of the contract;
The nature of the alleged breach;
The amount of alleged damages;
A description of the property against which the lien is intended to be imposed sufficient to identify the property, and stating the county or counties in which the property is located; and
A statement that the party against whose property the lien is intended to be imposed has the right to a hearing under subsection (c) of this section.
